{"tid":1373531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非！！！聽日同我出嚟遮打花園","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T16:06:20.000Z","uid":157301,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6b5dfe753314f3119052f171ecdf09492576d2d8","tid":1373531,"uid":157301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:41:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【和理非回合】 <br />\n聽日都有啊！！！！ <br />\n遮打花園係集會，唔係遊行，<br />\n三點至十一點，<br />\n***集會有不反對通知書***，<br />\n香港人出嚟接力喇！！！俾勇武班手足抖下，<br />\n已經有今日去咗全日嘅前線同我講，<br />\n聽日如果有咩事我都會再出黎，<br />\n野一次餐幾咁攰大家唔會唔知 <br />\n<br />\n聽日接力！！！！ <br />\n加油</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JH6JY3b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJH6JY3b.png&h=53a3f7b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NDzO99W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNDzO99W.png&h=1d6f4492&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/naVR7WE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnaVR7WE.png&h=b2f587ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hXAe5Jn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhXAe5Jn.png&h=4e6c7a4c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/18yTBP5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F18yTBP5.png&h=1734f977&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6ebf61220072c79407681692d2763f0018a1553","tid":1373531,"uid":157301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a373ed422e5714e224a155dfc7bce885d2b9895","tid":1373531,"uid":157301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:42:09.000Z","msg"